    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it! Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready to go and super reliable. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019d love to see it go to a good home. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
