    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and double VANOS for optimized volumetric efficiency across the powerband. Power is sent to the rear wheels through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock. The chassis remains composed with a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry perform as intended. Recent service includes a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment and a cooling system overhaul. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical vitals are robust, making this an ideal specimen for the purist driver seeking peak E46-era performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
