      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an expertly maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and disciplined ownership. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for performance and safety. While exhibiting the honest character of a seasoned road-goer, the exterior remains remarkably preserved, and the cabin retains a refined, professional atmosphere. This offering represents a sophisticated balance of proven reliability and exceptional value for the discerning driver who prioritizes long-term operational excellence.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
