      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been absolute gold. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super clean inside and drives like a dream. It\u2019s been well-loved and consistently maintained, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with its next owner right away! Perfect if you\u2019re looking for something dependable and stylish. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
